Testing #23286 

I am using the API `vscode.TextEdit.setEndOfLine` to change the end of line of a document. But the text edit that is being created from above API is removing the complete content from the file. I would expect this would only replace the end of line character of the document,

Here is my code

```ts
export function activate(context: vscode.ExtensionContext) {
    context.subscriptions.push(vscode.workspace.onWillSaveTextDocument(e => {
        if (e.document.eol === vscode.EndOfLine.CRLF) {
            const edit = vscode.TextEdit.setEndOfLine(vscode.EndOfLine.LF);
            e.waitUntil(Promise.resolve([edit]));
        } else {
            const edit = vscode.TextEdit.setEndOfLine(vscode.EndOfLine.CRLF);
            e.waitUntil(Promise.resolve([edit]));
        }
    }));
}
```

